'''保卫民主基金会'''（{{lang-en|Foundation for Defense of Democracies}}<ref name="《大事件》编辑部2016">{{cite book|author=《大事件》编辑部|title=《大事件》第59期: 问责各级一把手 怠政与腐败同罪|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=bbfEDAAAQBAJ&pg=PT188|date=2016-07-29|publisher=大事件杂志社|isbn=978-1-68182-152-8|pages=188–|access-date=2020-07-01|archive-date=2020-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200708162657/https://books.google.com/books?id=bbfEDAAAQBAJ&pg=PT188|dead-url=no}}</ref>，简写为'''FDD'''<ref name="Council2017">{{cite book|author=American Foreign Policy Council|title=The World Almanac of Islamism 2017|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=I8E6DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA1138|date=2017-12-18|publisher=Rowman & Littlefield Publishers|isbn=978-1-4422-7345-0|pages=1138–|access-date=2020-07-01|archive-date=2020-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200714141309/https://books.google.com/books?id=I8E6DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA1138|dead-url=no}}</ref>），又译作'''捍卫民主基金会'''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-china-polices-midterm-assessment/4767603.html|title=美智库给特朗普对华政策打分：打击侵犯知识产权有力，关注人权不足|date=2019年2月1日|publisher=[[美国之音|美国之音]]|accessdate=2020年7月1日|archive-date=2020年7月3日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703142833/https://www.voachinese.com/a/trump-china-polices-midterm-assessment/4767603.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一家[[总部|总部]]设在[[美国|美国]][[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]的[[501(c)(3)|501(c)(3)]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.charitynavigator.org/index.cfm?bay=search.irs&ein=134174402|title=Charity Navigator - IRS Data for Foundation for Defense of Democracies|website=Charity Navigator|language=en|access-date=2020-04-17|archive-date=2020-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200703125326/https://www.charitynavigator.org/index.cfm?bay=search.irs&ein=134174402|dead-url=no}}</ref>的非营利[[智库|智库]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/exclusive-huawei-whitehouse-1203-tues-idCNKBS1Y72TE|title=独家：白宫曾考虑将华为踢出美国金融体系--消息人士|date=2019年12月4日|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|accessdate=2020年7月1日|archive-date=2020年7月1日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200701144712/https://www.reuters.com/article/exclusive-huawei-whitehouse-1203-tues-idCNKBS1Y72TE|dead-url=no}}</ref>和政策研究所<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.charitynavigator.org/index.cfm?bay=search.summary&orgid=17166|title=Charity Navigator - Rating for Foundation for Defense of Democracies|website=Charity Navigator|language=en|access-date=2020-04-17|archive-date=2020-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200316141812/https://www.charitynavigator.org/index.cfm?bay=search.summary&orgid=17166|dead-url=no}}</ref>及游说组织<ref name="lobby-register">{{citation|first1=Aaron|last1=Schaffer|first2=Julian|last2=Pecquet|title=Anti-Iran advocacy group FDD registers to lobby|url=https://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2019/11/anti-iran-advocacy-group-fdd-registers-to-lobby.html|date=2019-11-15|access-date=|work=Al-Monitor|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191116031839/https://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2019/11/anti-iran-advocacy-group-fdd-registers-to-lobby.html|archive-date=2019-11-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该组织于2001成立，其[[政治倾向|政治倾向]]被划归为[[无党派|无党派]]<ref name=LATIMES>{{cite news|last=Richter|first=Paul|title=Chinese bank pulls out of Pakistan-Iran pipeline project|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2012/mar/14/world/la-fg-pakistan-china-pipeline-20120315|accessdate=2013-03-14|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=2012-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130301031248/http://articles.latimes.com/2012/mar/14/world/la-fg-pakistan-china-pipeline-20120315|archive-date=2013-03-01|url-status=|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[鹰派|鹰派]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2019/08/25/white-house-blindsided-by-iranian-foreign-minister-zarifs-g7-appearance.html |title=white house blindsided by iranian foreign minister zarif's appearance |last=Lee |first=Carol |publisher=[[CNBC|CNBC]] |accessdate= |url-status= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190920222612/https://www.cnbc.com/2019/08/25/white-house-blindsided-by-iranian-foreign-minister-zarifs-g7-appearance.html |archive-date=2019-09-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[新保守主义|新保守主义]]等<ref>{{cite news|last=Foster|first=Peter|title=Obama's new head boy|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/us-politics/9891755/Obamas-new-head-boy.html|accessdate=2013-03-12|newspaper=The Telegraph (UK)|date=2013-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130228034030/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/us-politics/9891755/Obamas-new-head-boy.html|archive-date=2013-02-28|url-status=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[中国大陆|中国大陆]]有[[学者|学者]]将其视为“[[美国价值观|美国价值观]]的积极倡导者”与“[[新保守主义|新保守主义]]堡垒”<ref>黄慧.{{cite web|url=http://www.mesi.shisu.edu.cn/_upload/article/3c/19/8c0e70634b5099104c05d05132c1/672919e8-a21c-4251-93a0-3552655cded4.pdf|title=中东剧变中的阿尔及利亚政局透视|date=2012年3月29日|publisher=阿拉伯世界研究|accessdate=2020年7月1日|archive-date=2020年7月2日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200702213441/http://www.mesi.shisu.edu.cn/_upload/article/3c/19/8c0e70634b5099104c05d05132c1/672919e8-a21c-4251-93a0-3552655cded4.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

保卫民主基金会每年都会举办各种各样的活动，包括年度华盛顿论坛，[[国会山|国会山]]简报会、为政府官员、外交官和军官举行的专家[[圆桌会议|圆桌会议]]、新书发布以及政策界内部的小组讨论和辩论等。

FDD发表关于[[外交政策|外交政策]]和[[安全问题|安全问题]]的[[研究报告|研究报告]]，重点关注[[核不扩散|核不扩散]]、[[网络威胁|网络威胁]]、[[制裁|制裁]]、[[非法金融|非法金融]]以及围绕[[朝鲜|朝鲜]]、[[伊朗|伊朗]]、[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]、[[阿富汗戰爭_(2001年－2021年)|阿富汗战争]]和其他研究领域的政策等主题<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://onthinktanks.org/think-tank/foundation-for-defense-of-democracies/|title=Foundation for Defense of Democracies|website=onthinktanks.org|language=|access-date=|archive-date=2021-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211207185623/https://onthinktanks.org/think-tank/foundation-for-defense-of-democracies/}}</ref>。
==历史与使命==
保卫民主基金会成立于2001年，就在[[九一一袭击事件|九一一袭击事件]]之后<ref name="Jett">{{citation|title=The Iran Nuclear Deal: Bombs, Bureaucrats, and Billionaires|first=Dennis C.|last=Jett|publisher=Springer|year=2017|isbn=9783319598222|page=83–86}}</ref>。在向[[美国国家税务局|美国国家税务局]]申请[[免税|免税]]地位的最初文件中，该组织称其使命是“提供教育，以提高[[以色列|以色列]]在[[北美|北美]]的[[形象|形象]]和[[公众|公众]]对影响以色列与阿拉伯关系的问题的理解”<ref name="Slate">{{citation|first=John B.|last=Judis|url=http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/foreigners/2015/08/foundation_for_the_defense_of_democracies_inside_the_small_pro_israel_think.html|title=The Little Think Tank That Could: Inside the small, pro-Israel outfit leading the attack on Obama’s Iran deal|work=Slate|date=18 August 2015|access-date=15 April 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150818220822/http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/foreigners/2015/08/foundation_for_the_defense_of_democracies_inside_the_small_pro_israel_think.single.html|archive-date=2015-08-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在它的网站上，FDD称自己是“一个非营利、无党派的501(c)3政策机构”，重点关注[[外交政策|外交政策]]和[[国家安全|国家安全]]，这些议题将政策研究、[[民主|民主]]和[[反恐|反恐]][[教育|教育]]、战略传播和[[调查报导|调查报导]]（investigative journalism）结合起来，以支持其促进[[多元主义|多元主义]]、捍卫[[民主价值|民主价值]]和打击[[恐怖主义|恐怖主义]]的[[意识形态|意识形态]]<ref name="Jett"/>。

根据美国《[[游说披露法|游说披露法]]》（Lobbying Disclousur Act of 1995，LDA），FDD于2019年11月15日正式注册为[[游说团体|游说团体]]<ref name="lobby-register"/>。
